        <b>Scheduled:</b>
        Wednesday, November 3, 2010 from 4:30 &ndash; 5:30pm 
        in 
        <a href="http://www.linuxplumbersconf.net/2010/ocw/events/LPC2010/rooms/9">Thomas Paine</a>
      </div>
    
